    <entry>
      <title>问题记录</title>
      <link href="/posts/59223.html"/>
      <url>/posts/59223.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note info flat"><p>本文记录一些折腾电脑(博客或者代码)遇到的问题和解决办法</p></div><h1 id="Win10-Win11关闭打开应用时弹出”打开文件-安全警告”弹框"><a href="#Win10-Win11关闭打开应用时弹出”打开文件-安全警告”弹框" class="headerlink" title="Win10/Win11关闭打开应用时弹出”打开文件-安全警告”弹框"></a><a href="https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2020343">Win10/Win11关闭打开应用时弹出”打开文件-安全警告”弹框</a></h1><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/65d64e447ad463846bdee5d4d07ed0e5.png" alt=""><br><div calss='anzhiyu-tag-link'><a class="tag-Link" target="_blank" href="/">    <div class="tag-link-tips">引用站外地址</div>    <div class="tag-link-bottom">        <div class="tag-link-left" style="background-image: url(https://api.iowen.cn/favicon/.png);"></div>        <div class="tag-link-right">            <div class="tag-link-title">Win10/Win11关闭打开应用时弹出"打开文件-安全警告"弹框</div>            <div class="tag-link-sitename"> https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2020343</div>        </div>        <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-angle-right"></i>    </div>    </a></div></p><h1 id="Github-Action-中的push的问题"><a href="#Github-Action-中的push的问题" class="headerlink" title="Github Action 中的push的问题"></a>Github Action 中的push的问题</h1><p>在Github Action中生成的一些文件，想把它推送到本仓库，然后发现一直报错<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Push to branch main</span><br><span class="line">remote: Permission to ***/blog-comic_pic.git denied to github-actions[bot].</span><br><span class="line">fatal: unable to access <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/***/blog-comic_pic.git/&#x27;</span>: The requested URL returned error: 403</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>只需要修改仓库中的Settings -&gt; Action -&gt; General -&gt; Workflow permissions<br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230807105305.png" alt=""></p><div calss='anzhiyu-tag-link'><a class="tag-Link" target="_blank" href="https://cdn.sstatic.net/Sites/stackoverflow/Img/favicon.ico?v=ec617d715196">    <div class="tag-link-tips">引用站外地址</div>    <div class="tag-link-bottom">        <div class="tag-link-left" style="background-image: url(https://api.iowen.cn/favicon/cdn.sstatic.net/Sites/stackoverflow/Img/favicon.ico?v=ec617d715196.png);"></div>        <div class="tag-link-right">            <div class="tag-link-title">Permission denied to github-actions[bot]. The requested URL returned error: 403</div>            <div class="tag-link-sitename"> https://stackoverflow.com/questions/73687176/permission-denied-to-github-actionsbot-the-requested-url-returned-error-403/75175628#75175628?newreg=f836aaef1ba94cad8e849905cee22db9</div>        </div>        <i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-angle-right"></i>    </div>    </a></div><details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 那些爱恨与情仇 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p>这是部署文件的内容，发现怎么推送不上去，找gpt，codeium，bing问了，回答都是啊github-actions[bot]，密钥没有权限啊啥的，啥狗屁玩意；我都准备放弃了，准备用后端的形式来推送给了，最后面才发现这么一篇文章。<br>PS：当时搜索结果还有好多显示是说上面密钥啥的问题，然后我发现这篇文章的网址是<br>stackoverflow.com的(为啥是他我就点进去了呢，之前我学过java一段时间，那时候在学习开发MC模组，然后遇到了个问题，前前后后也是找了好久，最终在这个网站里找到了解决办法，所以我才对这个网站有好感…一点犹豫都没有)，我就点进去看了，这一看，才解决，真的是，就这个问题，前前后后花我近一天的时间…<br>差不多这个样子，现在调不出来那个页面了<br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230807111653.png" alt=""><br><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Commit</span> <span class="string">files</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    git config --local user.email &quot;github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    git config --local user.name &quot;github-actions[bot]&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    git commit -m &quot;Add changes&quot; -a</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Push</span> <span class="string">changes</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">ad-m/github-push-action@master</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">with:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">github_token:</span> <span class="string">$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">secrets.GITHUBTOKEN</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Push to branch main</span><br><span class="line">remote: Permission to ***/blog-comic_pic.git denied to github-actions[bot].</span><br><span class="line">fatal: unable to access <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/***/blog-comic_pic.git/&#x27;</span>: The requested URL returned error: 403</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 看那些傻吊的回答 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230807105854.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230807105827.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230807105800.png" alt=""></p>              </div>            </details>              </div>            </details>]]></content>
      
      
