    <entry>
      <title>Vscode之个人优化篇（设置 | 插件）</title>
      <link href="/posts/16112.html"/>
      <url>/posts/16112.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>众所周知，vscode是一个非常好用的文本编辑器，通过各式各样的插件几乎是万能的，也可以作为好用的IDE，但vscode有很多默认不开启的、个人认为非常好用的一些设置，因此，在这里与大家分享，同时也推荐几个好用的插件。</p></blockquote><p>这篇文章的内容我会随着vscode的更新，做一些不定期的小修改。<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/"><span class='nota' data-nota='很好用'>Vscode官网</span></a></p><h2 id="推荐设置"><a href="#推荐设置" class="headerlink" title="推荐设置"></a><strong>推荐设置</strong></h2><p>下面是我的settings.json其中的一些基础配置<br><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;files.autoGuessEncoding&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;editor.smoothScrolling&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;workbench.list.smoothScrolling&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;terminal.integrated.smoothScrolling&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;editor.cursorSmoothCaretAnimation&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;explicit&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;editor.mouseWheelZoom&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;editor.suggestSelection&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;recentlyUsed&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;editor.acceptSuggestionOnEnter&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;smart&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;window.dialogStyle&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;custom&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">&quot;debug.showBreakpointsInOverviewRuler&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span><span class="punctuation">,</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h2 id="插件"><a href="#插件" class="headerlink" title="插件"></a><strong>插件</strong></h2><blockquote><p>插件种类繁多，对于各式各样的插件，我将我推荐的插件分成了四类，其中基础功能类是我认为在各种地方都很有帮助的插件，几乎可以是必备，其余的插件在很多情况下也很有用，可以按需安装</p></blockquote><div class="timeline  blue"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><strong>外观类</strong> </p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=GitHub.github-vscode-theme"><span class='nota' data-nota='软件皮肤'>Github Theme</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  GitHub 的官方主题,也是<u>目前在使用</u>(<span class='p blue'>Github Dark</span>)的，暗色系的主题，看着挺舒服的;在这里只选择几个看着挺不错的颜色主题作演示，其他的都太闪光弹了。。。<br>  <details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看主题效果 </summary>          <div class='content'>          <div class="tabs" id="theme"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#theme-1">Github Dark</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#theme-2">Github Dark Dimmed</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#theme-3">Github Light</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#theme-4">Other</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="theme-1"><p>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230730204926.png" alt="Github Dark"></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="theme-2"><p>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731082820.png" alt="Github Dark Dimmed"></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="theme-3"><p>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230730205008.png" alt="Github Light"></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="theme-4"><p>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731082752.png" alt="Github Dark Colorblind(Beta)"><br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230730205008.png" alt="Github Dark Default"><br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731082831.png" alt="Github Dark High Contrast"><br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230730205008.png" alt="Github Light Colorblind (Beta)"><br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731082849.png" alt="Github Light Default"><br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731082855.png" alt="Github Light High Contrast"></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="anzhiyufont anzhiyu-icon-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div>          </div>        </details></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=PKief.material-icon-theme"><span class='nota' data-nota='材质图标主题'>Material Icon Theme</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  一个材质图标主题，图标很好看！强烈推荐！<br>  <details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看材质图标效果 </summary>          <div class='content'>          <p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PKief/vscode-material-icon-theme/main/images/fileIcons.png" alt="File icons 文件图标"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PKief/vscode-material-icon-theme/main/images/folderIcons.png" alt="Folder icons 文件夹图标"></p>          </div>        </details>  </p></div></div></div><div class="timeline  blue"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><strong>基础功能类</strong> </p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=MS-CEINTL.vscode-language-pack-zh-hans"><span class='nota' data-nota='中国人必备好吧'>Chinese (Simplified) (简体中文)</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  [中文语言包]这应该不用多介绍，是vscode的官方中文语言包<br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731182030.png" alt=""></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=usernamehw.errorlens"><span class='nota' data-nota='挺不错的'>Error Lens</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  【错误提示】可以将原先显示的问题显示在对应行右侧并高亮<br>  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/usernamehw/vscode-error-lens/master/img/demo.png" alt=""></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=christian-kohler.path-intellisense"><span class='nota' data-nota='用了就回不去了'>Path Intellisense</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  【路径补全】在输入路径时，有智能提示补全<br>  <img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230731182957.png" alt=""></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=kisstkondoros.vscode-gutter-preview"><span class='nota' data-nota='有这个挺方便的'>Image preview</span></a></p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>  【图像预览】可以预览引入的图像<br>  <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kisstkondoros/gutter-preview/master/images/sample.png" alt=""></p></div></div></div><p>…未完待续</p><blockquote><p>一些参考链接</p><ul><li><a href="https://www.fomal.cc/posts/2013454d.html">Markdown语法与外挂标签写法汇总</a></li></ul></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
