    <entry>
      <title>番剧重构记录</title>
      <link href="/posts/63052.html"/>
      <url>/posts/63052.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="番剧重构记录"><a href="#番剧重构记录" class="headerlink" title="番剧重构记录"></a>番剧重构记录</h1><div class="timeline blue"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p><a href="/comic/">HTT</a></p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-08-06</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>初步实现了番剧后端的处理</li><li>目前需要完善的点有：<br>[急需]在图床那里添加部署流(自动获取图片的信息)<br>后端添加上传图片的功能<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看效果 </summary>            <div class='content'>            <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230806230507.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230806230527.png" alt=""></p>            </div>          </details></li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-07-29</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>重写了获取B站追番数据的脚本</li><li>生成页面的架构也重写了</li><li>本页面基本上功能都有了，没什么大的Bug了<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 查看效果 </summary>            <div class='content'>            <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/2023-07-29-20-19.gif" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/2023-07-29-20-20.gif" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/2023-07-29-20-21.gif" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/2023-07-29-20-32.gif" alt=""></p>            </div>          </details></li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-07-28</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>修复了<a href="#目前存在的Bug">在博客里查看番剧页面，页面没能成功渲染出来</a>的BUG<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 查看效果 </summary>            <div class='content'>            <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230728132057.png" alt=""></p>            </div>          </details></li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-07-27</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>根据<a href="https://kmar.top/posts/456efd20/">给博客添加追番页面</a>重构了获取番剧信息的脚本</li><li>根据<a href="https://www.adicw.cn/comic">Χαλαρό - 动漫</a>写了大部分的页面渲染<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看效果 </summary>            <div class='content'>            <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230727161051.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230727161913.png" alt=""></p>            </div>          </details></li></ul></div></div></div><h1 id="目前存在的Bug"><a href="#目前存在的Bug" class="headerlink" title="目前存在的Bug"></a>目前存在的Bug</h1><div class="timeline blue"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>BUG现状</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-07-29</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>生成详细页面的时候，底部的页面还能滑动<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看BUG情况 </summary>            <div class='content'>            <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/2023-07-29-20-40.gif" alt=""></p>            </div>          </details></li></ul></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2023-07-27</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><ul><li>在博客里查看番剧页面，页面没能成功渲染出来，哔哩头图也没能成功加载，数据也没能成功读取，有可能是PJAX的<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看BUG情况 </summary>           <div class='content'>           <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230727161136.png" alt=""></p>           </div>         </details>- 在选择tag的时候页脚的页数没能成功渲染出来，上一页和下一页按钮也没能正常禁用<details class="folding-tag" blue><summary> 点击查看BUG情况 </summary>           <div class='content'>           <p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/Azumic/blog_pic@main/page_img/20230727161230.png" alt=""></p>           </div>         </details></li></ul></div></div></div>]]></content>
      
      
